OL,3,CPatients call for hospital waiting
OL,4,Clist clarity
OL,6,FDr Nigel Minihane, a Jersey GP, says:
OL,7,F"Patients should actually be able to
OL,8,Fsee where they are on the waiting list
OL,9,F- not just the waiting list.
OL,11,F"With the technology we have at the
OL,12,Fmoment - it shouldn't be a far fetched
OL,13,Fthing to give people information ...
OL,14,Fwhy shouldn't our island be able to do
OL,15,Fthat?"
OL,17,FDr Nigel Minihane: "Fudging the issue
OL,18,Fis not something that we should be
OL,19,Fdoing"
